"Project-Id-Version: tina4-python\n"
"Report-Msgid-Bugs-To: \n"
"POT-Creation-Date: 2025-03-05 00:00+0200\n"
"PO-Revision-Date: 2025-03-05 00:00+0200\n"
"Last-Translator: Tina4 Team\n"
"Language: ja\n"
"Language-Team: ja\n"
"Plural-Forms: nplurals=1; plural=0;\n"
